could also have an impact

00:08:08.435 --> 00:08:12.040
on decreasing service utilization cost

00:08:12.040 --> 00:08:14.392
and economic broaden more broadly.

00:08:14.392 --> 00:08:18.850
One of the big challenges
related to early detection

00:08:18.850 --> 00:08:20.930
or one of the critique's
people might have is the risk

00:08:20.930 --> 00:08:24.917
of false positives, so
identifying a child as having

00:08:24.917 --> 00:08:28.051
